{"title":"噪音增加日（图片）","authors":["夏清泉","元也"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":11,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"噪音增加日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏清泉画  元也诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐鸣的歌乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喧闹的锣鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喇叭里震天的吼叫："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天是减少噪音日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了环境，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了身体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把噪音减少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真可悲太可笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹得响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲得凶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喊得高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂不正是把噪音制造。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此悲喜剧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南辕北辙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越帮越忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愈演愈糟！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}